            "type": "text.done",
            "content": "Here are the **top breaking news stories today, March 14, 2026**:\n\n---\n\n## 🌍 Middle East — US-Israel War on Iran (Day 15)\n\n- The United States-Israel war on Iran, now in its third week, continues to escalate after US forces struck military targets on Kharg Island, the critical hub through which most of Iran's crude exports pass.\n\n- President Donald Trump said the US \"totally obliterated every military target\" on Kharg Island, which handles roughly 90% of Iran's crude exports.\n\n- US President Donald Trump said Washington deliberately spared the island's oil infrastructure but warned that it could be attacked if Iran interferes with shipping through the Strait of Hormuz.\n\n- Vice President JD Vance said that Iran's new supreme leader Mojtaba Khamenei is \"hurt,\" but it's unclear if the United States is responsible.\n\n---\n\n## 🇱🇧 Lebanon\n\n- Israeli attacks have killed at least 773 people in Lebanon since March 2. Lebanon's Health Ministry strongly condemned an Israeli strike on a healthcare centre in Borj Qalaouiye that killed 12 medical staff, including doctors, nurses, and paramedics.\n\n- Israeli shells also struck the headquarters of a Nepalese peacekeeping battalion serving with UNIFIL in the southern Lebanese town of Meiss el-Jabal.\n\n---\n\n## 🇮🇶 Iraq\n\n- The U.S. military confirmed that four service members were killed in the crash of a U.S. refueling plane in Iraq.\n\n- Iraq says a helipad at the US Embassy in Baghdad has been hit by a missile.\n\n---\n\n## 🇺🇸 US Domestic\n\n- U.S. Transportation Security Administration security officers missed their first full paycheck as a partial funding shutdown of the government approached the one-month mark.\n\n---\n\n## 🇮🇳 India\n\n- 5 Indians have been killed and one is missing in the West Asia conflict so far; the Ministry of External Affairs says Indian Missions in the region are open 24/7.\n\n---\n\nThese are rapidly evolving stories. Stay tuned to major news outlets for the latest updates.\n\n---\n**Citations:**\n- [Iran war: What is happening on day 15 of US-Israel attacks? | US-Israel war on Iran News | Al Jazeera](https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/3/14/iran-war-what-is-happening-on-day-15-of-us-israel-attacks)\n- [News: U.S. and World News Headlines : NPR](https://www.npr.org/sections/news/)\n- [Top of the Morning, March 14, 2026 | Local News | news-gazette.com](https://www.news-gazette.com/news/local/community-events/top-of-the-morning-march-14-2026/article_11d60039-04af-4a13-8361-3bd3c6d224bf.html)\n- [[Highlights] Breaking News Today,11 March 2026: Lok Sabha rejects opposition's No Confidence Motion against Speaker Om Birla](https://news24online.com/india/breaking-news-live-updates-march-11-2026-iran-israel-donald-trump-khamenei-abu-dhabi-pm-modi-congress-bjp-parliament-budget-session-air-india-fuel-charges-latest-news-today/771524/)\n- [Video. Latest news bulletin | March 14th, 2026 – Midday | Euronews](https://www.euronews.com/video/2026/03/14/latest-news-bulletin-march-14th-2026-midday)\n- [5 Big News Stories Overnight - Saturday, March 14, 2026](https://www.golocalprov.com/news/5-big-news-stories-overnight-saturday-march-14-2026)\n- [Stories from March 14, 2026 | MPR News](https://www.mprnews.org/content/3-14-2026)\n- [Day 14 of Middle East conflict — Trump says US ‘totally obliterated every military target’ at Iran oil hub | CNN](https://www.cnn.com/world/live-news/iran-war-us-israel-trump-03-13-26)\n- [Latest Breaking News Videos | Fox News Video](https://www.foxnews.com/video)\n- [PBS News: News, Analysis, Top Headlines, Live Coverage](https://www.pbs.org/newshour/)"
